        <h1>About Facemash</h1>
        <hr>
        <h2>Welcome to Facemash!</h2>
        <p>Facemash is a dynamic, engaging platform designed to connect people through the power of visual comparison. Inspired by the early concepts of social networking, our app brings a fresh twist to interacting with images of friends, colleagues, and acquaintances. Whether you’re here to see how people stack up against each other or to discover new connections, Facemash offers a unique and interactive experience.</p>

        <hr>
        <h1>Our Vision</h1>
        <p>At Facemash, we believe that the way we perceive and interact with images can open up new avenues for connection and understanding. We aim to create an environment where users can engage with content in a fun and meaningful way, sparking conversations and fostering relationships through visual interaction.</p>

        <hr>
        <h1>Features</h1>
        <ul>
            <li>Image Comparisons: Engage with a variety of images and participate in side-by-side comparisons. Cast your votes and see how others feel!</li>
            <li>Discover New Faces: Browse through profiles and images to meet new people and explore different perspectives.</li>
            <li>Personalized Experience: Customize your interaction with the app based on your preferences and interests.</li>
        </ul>

        <hr>
        <h1>Privacy and Security</h1>
        <p>Your privacy is important to us. Facemash is designed with robust privacy settings to ensure that your personal information and interactions remain secure. We adhere to the highest standards of data protection and are committed to creating a safe environment for all our users.</p>

        <hr>
        <h1>Join Us</h1>
        <p>Become a part of the Facemash community and experience a new way of connecting with others. Whether you're here to see how your friends fare in image comparisons or to explore new social dynamics, we’re excited to have you on board!</p>
        <p>Thank you for choosing Facemash!</p>
